  "body": "What do you think about adding another ticker to `w.update` that will periodically rebuild bloom filter from currently \"live\" filters?\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nBloom filter is changed at least periodically to reflect the current state of topics used by consumers filters.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nBloom filter is not updated when Unscubscribe is called. Which means that the node will be consuming unnecessary traffic, and the only way to get rid of it would be a restart of the whisper or re-create bloom filter from scratch.\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\nSee attached unit test.\r\n",
